        <h1>ELH Bash example</h1>
        <p>Runs the following Bash script on the server, similar to PHP</p>
        <pre><code>
    <pur>for</pur> file <pur>in</pur> <pin>$(</pin><blu>ls</blu><pin>)</pin><dar>;</dar> <pur>do</pur>
        <red>printf<red> <gre>"&lt;p&gt;<pin>${</pin><mag>file</mag><pin>}</pin><gre>&lt;/p&gt;\n"</gre>
    <pur>done</pur>
        </code></pre>
        <h2>The output:</h2>
        <$bash
            for file in $(ls); do
              printf "<p>$file</p>\n"
            done
          $>
